title: Savage Lands v0.2.7
description:
FIXED:

    Fixed several stability issues and crashes



ADDED:
General:

    When new characters are created, items needed to survive are no longer hidden in the player's inventory at start but instead can be found nearby on the beach.
    New character Survival Tips UI added to right hand side of the screen.
    Players can turn off Survival Tips from rendering in their settings menu


Crafting

    Primitive Flint Axe now available for crafting
